'.\" -*- nroff -*-
.TH KAFSIMAGE 8 "2026-03-04" "kafs 0.2.3" "System Administration"
.SH NAME
kafsimage \- export offline KAFS image data in metadata-only mode
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B kafsimage
.B --metadata-only
.RB [ --verify ]
.I src-image
.I dst-file
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B kafsimage
reads an offline source image and writes a metadata-only export file.
Current v0 behavior copies the metadata prefix
.IR [0, first_data_block * block_size) .
The source image is never modified.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B --metadata-only
Enable metadata-only export mode.
.TP
.B --verify
After export, verify destination bytes match the copied source prefix.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Export succeeded.
.TP
.B 1
I/O, bounds, or verification failure.
.TP
.B 2
Usage error.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR kafsdump (8),
.BR fsck.kafs (8),
.BR mkfs.kafs (8)
.SH AUTHOR
kafs project.
